{
  "stem": "942.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I remember there were signs in Auschwitz, you know, a big sign that one louse-- you know, lice, you know-- could be your death, you know.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So you know, you tried hard, you know, you-- but we had to wash our own jackets and stuff like that, you know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We didn't get any clean underwear.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "There was no underwear, you see.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when we came back at night, we received our rations.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And supper was a cup of coffee.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We call it ersatz coffee, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It looked like coffee.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we received a slice of bread that was about a quarter inch thick-- that was mostly, it was crumbling away-- and a little square of margarine.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was our diet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some nights instead of margarine, they gave us a little spoon of something that looked like jam, you know.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was made from some artificial stuff.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was our diet, day in and day out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On Sunday, lunch was the main meal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At lunch time, we had a soup, and they gave about three, four little potatoes like that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was the diet.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And from what I gather, it was less than 300 calories a day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So you know, we were so hungry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "After a week or two, you know, the hunger was so bad that-- and, you know, I had a dilemma, what to do with this bread every night, you know.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because if I ate the whole piece, you know, I had nothing left for the next day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I had to decide that I'm only taking a couple of little bites.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I had a [NON-ENGLISH], a rag, you know, that I used to roll this bread into this rag and keep it for the next day.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
